				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">well it is possible for an sk to tank all the way through the sewer trials, mountain trials, and the kod taz trials.  <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=536041" target="_blank" class="postlink">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=536041</a>  is the magelo of the sk who did it in my guild.  of course he did have 2 clerics in the groups and he is the best geared sk on the server and had max preGoD aa's and lots of aa's in GoD now(754 aa's total).  there are a couple of tricks used also (he didn't tank the whole time.. another class did the first 20% or so on the bosses - i'll leave it to you to figure that out )  and also its important to have items with +shielding.  now granted, he's one of the better geared sk's serverwide (#10 serverwide hp wise) so most sk's won't be doing this anytime soon.. just saying it is possible with lots of gear, skill, aa's, healing, and of course luck.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=99608" target="_blank" class="postlink">Daetien Beyazid</a> 
