				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Wizards are amazing in Sewers in that they can evac, snare (two vital roles) and they have great burst DPS. With max GoD AAs and flappy and the wiz in my group last night was very regularly hitting 6k+ nukes.  Two of those and the mob is dead very quick.  I am lucky to hit 2 x 2k damage rock of taelosia before they are dead, in which case they are outdamaging me and my pet by a VERY large margin.
<br />

<br />
Rogues with SoS are very useful indeed, and also damage like crazy. 
<br />

<br />
The only thing we mages can pull out besides subpar DPS is Call of the Hero.   <img src="images/smiles/icon_cry.gif" alt="Crying or Very sad" border="0" /><br />_________________<br />Kimberly Shaw
