<br />

<br />
Heh, well *I* can tank mtns+ with a good slower and 3-4 healers...the point is though, how much do we have to invest in that 6 person group to keep a single tanking person up?  If it requires minimum 3 other classes to keep a single tank up then that tank is not viable.
<br />

<br />
In general, warrior is the only one who can tank with just 1 cleric.  A knight needs a cleric and druid minimum, and a ranger, gah 2 clerics at least.  So every slot you fill trying to make the tank viable is one less slot you have for *everyone else* ie the support and DPS classes.
<br />

<br />
This is the root of the problem of GoD past the sewers.
